{
  "stem": "21139.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only that they were contacting the-- the Red Cross in Paris, and I will hear from them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I heard from them eventually where they said that they were-- my parents were shipped towards Auschwitz, and they did not return.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was in-- when I was in England, in London, there's a Jewish-- was a Jewish organization, and it was called the Bloomsbury House, and it was on Bloomsbury Street.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I suppose that's why the-- the name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It must have been the OSE that also contacted them that I-- that I would like to go to England where my sister and my brothers were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they assisted me then-- from then on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I-- I remember so well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I made up my mind I'm not going to clean the floors for the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going to learn something, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to study whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since-- since childhood, I always wanted to go into nursing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told that to the people in London, if there's a possibility that I could go into training for that profession.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- but they said, it will take a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And first of all, I had to finish high school, which I had not finished-- I-- which I did later on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I went into training, but there I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went-- took that course for newborn care and nursery school teaching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What I should have done-- even so, it took an additional year to take as a registered nurse, to train for that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I had no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had nothing to wear practically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to make a living for myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I want to do something the fastest way that I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
